  "detailed_description": "<i><strong>Tower Fall </strong></i> is a fun PC alternative to the board game known as \"falling tower\". The principle is quite simple: a tower is built from even bars (each new “floor” is made with alternating laying direction and consists of 3 bars), and then the players begin to carefully pull out one bar at a time and put it on top of the tower. The one who loses in the game, after the course of which, the tower fell.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features:</h2>- 3 types of game:<br>* game against artificial intelligence<br>* game between two people<br>* scoring game<br>- different types of locations<br>- several types of bars<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094720/extras/5668d29e14a9746a6cd737e45dfbd726.avif?t=1660139053\" width=600 height=196 /></span>",
